    <title>树莓派3B+设置静态IP</title>
    <link href="https://qishilmx.github.io/cjso7ledt0001p4fdq0duodjx/"/>
    <id>https://qishilmx.github.io/cjso7ledt0001p4fdq0duodjx/</id>
    <published>2019-02-24T16:29:44.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-02-27T08:59:06.392Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><!-- build time:Thu Feb 28 2019 13:49:27 GMT+0800 (GMT+08:00) --><a id="more"></a><p>执行</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/dhcpcd.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>在文件末尾添加</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span>有线静态ip设置</span><br><span class="line">interface eth0</span><br><span class="line">static ip_address=192.168.0.53/24 #IPV4的地址</span><br><span class="line">static ip6_address=fd51:42f8:caae:d92e::ff/64 #IPV6的地址</span><br><span class="line">static routers=192.168.0.1 #网关</span><br><span class="line">static domain_name_servers=192.168.0.1 8.8.8.8 fd51:42f8:caae:d92e::1 #DNS</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span>无线静态IP设置</span><br><span class="line">interface wlan0</span><br><span class="line">static ip_address=192.168.0.53/24 #PV4的地址</span><br><span class="line">static ip6_address=fd51:42f8:caae:d92e::ff/64 #IPV6的地址</span><br><span class="line">static routers=192.168.0.1 #网关</span><br><span class="line">static domain_name_servers=192.168.0.1 8.8.8.8 fd51:42f8:caae:d92e::1 #DNS</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
    
